OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780301370
OL,3,CStonemason's widow fears quartz
OL,4,Cworktops are 'next asbestos health
OL,5,Ccrisis'
OL,7,FThe family of a stonemason fears the
OL,8,Findustrial lung disease which killed
OL,9,Fhim could be "the next asbestos health
OL,10,Fcrisis".
OL,12,FGeorge Elliot died from silicosis aged
OL,13,F64 after four decades installing stone
OL,14,Fslabs in buildings around the world.
OL,16,FTradespeople are particularly
OL,17,Fvulnerable to the condition, which is
OL,18,Fcaused by inhaling large quantities of
OL,19,Ftoxic silica dust.
OL,26,@qD@NOUrD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780301370
OL,3,CStonemason's widow fears quartz
OL,4,Cworktops are 'next asbestos health
OL,5,Ccrisis'
OL,7,FLeading doctors are linking a rapid
OL,8,Frise in cases to the increasing
OL,9,Fpopularity of engineered stone ` also
OL,10,Fknown as quartz ` in new kitchens and
OL,11,Fbathrooms.
OL,13,FWhile marble contains less than five
OL,14,Fper cent crystalline silica, the
OL,15,Fartificial stone can contain up to 95
OL,16,Fper cent, according to Dr Jo Feary.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780301370
OL,3,CStonemason's widow fears quartz
OL,4,Cworktops are 'next asbestos health
OL,5,Ccrisis'
OL,7,FThe respiratory consultant at the
OL,8,FRoyal Brompton Hospital told ITV News:
OL,9,F"We have seen a real uplift in cases
OL,10,Fof silicosis due to engineered stone,
OL,11,Faround the world since 2010.
OL,13,F"We would say there is now a global
OL,14,Fepidemic of this disease ` with over
OL,15,F5,000 cases around the world."
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@AOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780301370
OL,3,CStonemason's widow fears quartz
OL,4,Cworktops are 'next asbestos health
OL,5,Ccrisis'
OL,7,FInhaling silica dust causes a
OL,8,Fprogressive scarring of the lungs, for
OL,9,Fwhich there is no cure. The Royal
OL,10,FBrompton in west London has set-up a
OL,11,Fdedicated clinic in response to the
OL,12,Fsurge in cases.
OL,14,FDr Feary added: "If engineered stone
OL,15,Fproducts are present in your home, in
OL,16,Fyour building, in your workplace,
OL,17,Fthey're not going to cause you any
OL,18,Fharm."
OL,26,@vD@QOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780301370
OL,3,CStonemason's widow fears quartz
OL,4,Cworktops are 'next asbestos health
OL,5,Ccrisis'
OL,7,F"The risk is to people who are
OL,8,Fcutting, grinding and polishing these
OL,9,Fproducts over several months and
OL,10,Fyears."
OL,12,FGeorge Elliott's widow, Sandra, is now
OL,13,Fcampaigning for a change in the law to
OL,14,Fbetter protect workers from the
OL,15,Fdangers of silica dust.
OL,17,FThe couple were together for 34 years
OL,18,Fand moved from Croydon in south London
OL,19,Fto Bexhill-on-Sea in East Sussex in
OL,20,F2022.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780301370
OL,3,CStonemason's widow fears quartz
OL,4,Cworktops are 'next asbestos health
OL,5,Ccrisis'
OL,7,FSandra recalls: "It was a lovely time
OL,8,Fbecause we moved down to Sussex
OL,9,Fthinking we were going to have a
OL,10,Flovely time and relax but in 2023 his
OL,11,Fhealth really started to deteriorate."
OL,13,FSandra added: "His health deteriorated
OL,14,Fso quickly. He was on oxygen all the
OL,15,Ftime. Poor Goerge was just shattered
OL,16,Fand you wouldn't want anyone to see
OL,17,Fit."
OL,26,@oD@QOUsD@fO]uD@OOUyD@DO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780301370
OL,3,CStonemason's widow fears quartz
OL,4,Cworktops are 'next asbestos health
OL,5,Ccrisis'
OL,7,F"I just love him and miss him so much.
OL,8,FI don't want people to be suffering
OL,9,Flike me. It's so upsetting to see
OL,10,Fsomeone that you can't help who is
OL,11,Fgoing to die."
OL,13,FThe Health and Safety Executive
OL,14,Fpublished new guidance, last month,
OL,15,Fbanning the dry cutting of engineered
OL,16,Fstone in an effort to protect workers.
OL,18,FThe HSE states that businesses must
OL,19,Fuse water to suppress dust during the
OL,20,Fcutting of artificial stone, in order
OL,21,Fto meet legal requirements.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780301370
OL,3,CStonemason's widow fears quartz
OL,4,Cworktops are 'next asbestos health
OL,5,Ccrisis'
OL,7,FThe Worktop Fabricators Federation
OL,8,Fdescribed the new guidelines as a
OL,9,F"level playing field" and suggested
OL,10,Fconsumers could help make sure they
OL,11,Fare being followed.
OL,13,FWFF operations officer, Nigel
OL,14,FFletcher, told ITV News: "If it sounds
OL,15,Ftoo good to be true and the price is
OL,16,Flow: question it. If they are a
OL,17,Fresponsible fabricator there is a cost
OL,18,Finvolved in that process."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@UO]vD@ZOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780301370
OL,3,CStonemason's widow fears quartz
OL,4,Cworktops are 'next asbestos health
OL,5,Ccrisis'
OL,7,FUnite the union has started an online
OL,8,Fpetition calling for a total ban on
OL,9,Fthe installation of quartz worktops in
OL,10,FBritish buildings. Australia outlawed
OL,11,Fthe supply and manufacture of
OL,12,Fengineered stone in 2024.
OL,14,F"This is the next asbestosis health
OL,15,Fcrisis, as far as I'm concerned," said
OL,16,FGeorge Elliott's sister-in-law
OL,17,FCaroline Hudson.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780301370
OL,3,CStonemason's widow fears quartz
OL,4,Cworktops are 'next asbestos health
OL,5,Ccrisis'
OL,7,F"All of us are having this engineered
OL,8,Fstone in our homes and I don't think
OL,9,Fthe general public know what goes on
OL,10,Fbehind the scenes."
OL,12,FAsked whether the comparison with
OL,13,Fasbestos was helpful, Dr Jo Feary
OL,14,Fsaid: "I think a lot of people know
OL,15,Fabout the dangers of asbestos.
OL,16,FSilicosis is another occupational lung
OL,17,Fdisease.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@SO]vD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780301370
OL,3,CStonemason's widow fears quartz
OL,4,Cworktops are 'next asbestos health
OL,5,Ccrisis'
OL,7,F"So, if (the comparison) helps raise
OL,8,Fawareness of the hazards and dangers
OL,9,Fof breathing in dust in the workplace,
OL,10,Fthen absolutely (it is helpful)."
OL,12,FCaroline Hudson's local MP has secured
OL,13,Fa parliamentary debate this week on
OL,14,Fsilica dust exposure in the workplace.
OL,16,FLiz Jarvis, the Lib Dem MP for
OL,17,FEastleigh, has previously proposed new
OL,18,Flegislation in the House of Commons on
OL,19,Fthe prevention, monitoring, and
OL,20,Freporting of silicosis.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@IpmoD@XpnrD@QpmrD@_pn
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780301370
OL,3,CStonemason's widow fears quartz
OL,4,Cworktops are 'next asbestos health
OL,5,Ccrisis'
OL,7,FLiz Jarvis told ITV News: "There needs
OL,8,Fto be a huge public awareness
OL,9,Fcampaign. Silicosis is completely
OL,10,Fpreventable.
OL,12,F"We've got to make sure that all the
OL,13,Ffacts are in the public domain and
OL,14,Fthat everyone can get access to PPE
OL,15,Fand that they will be protected from
OL,16,Fgetting this awful disease."
OL,26,@oD@[OUtD@AOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
