OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780301370
OL,3,CStonemason's widow fears quartz
OL,4,Cworktops are 'next asbestos health
OL,5,Ccrisis'
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,8,FWork and Pensions said: "Our
OL,9,Fcondolences are with anyone who has
OL,10,Flost a loved one to silicosis or been
OL,11,Faffected by work-related disease.
OL,13,F"We're tackling this issue head-on.
OL,14,FThe Health and Safety Executive will
OL,15,Fbe enforcing new guidance it recently
OL,16,Fpublished to drive up standards across
OL,17,Fthe industry and make sure the lives
OL,18,Fof workers are protected."
OL,26,@pD@YOUuD@AOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/14
